1. Make sure your computer has a C language compiler and executionable environment.
2. Either manually compile the code or use the Makefile file
3. When the code is correctly compiled and run, "Word to count: " message will pop up
4. Enter the word that you seek to find
5. Enter the sentence you seek to find the word from
6. Examine the results
7. Enter "quit" when the program asks to input the word in order to terminate the program
